{
  "id": "RAW_427a2b01",
  "title": "如何在一个 OpenClaw 中同时养多只龙虾🦞，并打通多个飞书 Bot",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI2NzM4MTQwMg==&mid=2247494216&idx=1&sn=cfa0ec55c59dbab5ba6240afcd7bdf00",
  "date": "2026-03-07 09:37:00",
  "author": "Draco",
  "siteName": "Draco正在VibeCoding",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ddd66331&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F0m9F5vC1OGgbStBicRgPXrIffZFMGqWmlzgrwJySicAaicv9Pltfye2rbzBp1dNZHs3ePvlAWBUZKzTwmJXfSKNEicyZlCB7WVyuLKxRx3eywwA%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\" style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"></p>\n  <div style=\"font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif;font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.75;text-align: left;\">\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-top:0 !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">OpenClaw原生支持在一个实例下安装多个Agent（并行多只🦞）。每个Agent可以对应不同聊天软件的渠道channel。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;\"><span leaf=\"\">今天以同一个OpenClaw实例下2个Agents对应2个不同的飞书Bot为例进行讲解。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;\"><span leaf=\"\">原则上同时养3只、4只、5只、N只龙虾🦞都可以，就看你的硬件配置有多夯了~ &nbsp;</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;\"><span leaf=\"\">废话不多说，步骤如下：</span></p>\n   <h2 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"display: table;margin: 4em auto 2em;color: #fff;background: #FA5151;font-weight: bold;text-align: center;padding: 0.3em 1.2em;font-size: 19.5px;border-radius: 8px 24px 8px 24px;box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);\"><span leaf=\"\">一、在飞书中创建新的Bot应用</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;display:block;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:1em;\"><span leaf=\"\">之前已经写过太多次了，请参考之前文章中的步骤吧~</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"list-style-type: circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin:0;display:block;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI2NzM4MTQwMg==&amp;mid=2247493923&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=ace7294883a492ae6b182bc58a54c823&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"低门槛的OpenClaw🦞来了！我用5分钟做了一个7x24小时的股市盯盘助⼿～\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">低门槛的OpenClaw🦞来了！我用5分钟做了一个7x24小时的股市盯盘助⼿～</a></span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin:0;display:block;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI2NzM4MTQwMg==&amp;mid=2247493608&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=d168b389f053c434b2f05271f6f2a94d&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"（可能全网最全/长的）2万字Openclaw保姆教程\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">（可能全网最全/长的）2万字Openclaw保姆教程</a></span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;display:block;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:1em;\"><span leaf=\"\">最后的交付物是</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif;font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.75;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;display:block;font-size:1em;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:#3f3f3f;margin:0;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">新建飞书Bot应用的<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 76, 65);font-weight: bold;\">AppID和AppSecret&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\">请务必保存好。</span></p>\n   <h2 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"display: table;margin: 4em auto 2em;color: #fff;background: #FA5151;font-weight: bold;text-align: center;padding: 0.3em 1.2em;font-size: 19.5px;border-radius: 8px 24px 8px 24px;box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);\"><span leaf=\"\">二、在OpenClaw中添加刚才新建的飞书channel</span></h2>\n   <ul style=\"margin-left:0;padding-left:1.5em;list-style:none;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"margin:0.5em 8px;display:block;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">• 打开openclaw安装目录中的 openclaw.json 文件；Mac和Linux一般都在根目录下的.openclaw目录下，即&nbsp;</span><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">~</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__regexp\">/.openclaw/</span></span><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">openclaw.</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__property\">json</span></span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <ul style=\"margin-left:0;padding-left:1.5em;list-style:none;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"margin:0.5em 8px;display:block;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">• 找到channels所在的字段：</span></p>\n     <figure style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"GxD5qv\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3907407407407407\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\";\" data-imgfileid=\"100010545\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f824eec6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F0m9F5vC1OGhlkQYoCqRdLMiaSVhDgAZMwebVQBZibrRCsuM3QzIuESniaZDBibXWrXvyuMyukDmfYpiaSia5dN2D8qJGu0X3g5zD6Zic3ciasOHF7WQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n      <figcaption style=\"text-align: center;color: #888;font-size: 0.8em;\"></figcaption>\n     </figure>\n     <p></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin:0.5em 8px;display:block;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">• 将其修改为：</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <pre style=\"border-radius:8px;border:1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);padding:0 !important;margin:10px 8px;font-size:90%;overflow-x:auto;line-height:1.5;\"><code style=\"border-radius:4px;padding:0.5em 1em 1em;margin:0;text-indent:0;white-space:nowrap;display:-webkit-box;font-size:90%;overflow-x:auto;font-family:'Fira Code',\n    Menlo,\n    Operator Mono,\n    Consolas,\n    Monaco,\n    monospace;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">\"channels\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\">:</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;{</span><span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; \"feishu\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\">:</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;{</span><span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; \"enabled\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\">:</span><span><span><span leaf=\"\">true</span></span></span><span leaf=\"\">,</span><span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; \"defaultAccount\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\">:</span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;\"default\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\">,</span><span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; \"connectionMode\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\">:</span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;\"websocket\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\">,</span><span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; \"domain\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\">:</span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;\"feishu\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\">,</span><span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; \"groupPolicy\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\">:</span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;\"disabled\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\">,</span><span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; \"accounts\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\">:</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;{</span><span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; \"default\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\">:</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;{</span><span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; \"appId\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\">:</span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;\"之前已经存在的飞书 bot 的 ID\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\">,</span><span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; \"appSecret\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\">:</span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;\"之前已经存在的飞书 bot 的 secret\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; }</span><span leaf=\"\">,</span><span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; \"ops\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\">:</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;{</span><span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; \"appId\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\">:</span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;\"新建的飞书 bot 的 appId\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\">,</span><span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; \"appSecret\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\">:</span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;\"新建的飞书 bot 的 appSecret\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; }</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; }</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; }</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">}</span></code></pre>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;\"><span leaf=\"\">这里有两个关键点：</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"margin-left:0;padding-left:1.5em;list-style:none;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"margin:0.5em 8px;display:block;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">• 把你现在顶层的 appId / appSecret 挪进 accounts.default（挪进去之后删除原来位置的appId和appSecret否则会出问题）；</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin:0.5em 8px;display:block;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">• 新增一个 accounts.ops（假设这个新添加的飞书子渠道的名字是‘ops’）；</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <figure style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"2eEXb6\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6648148148148149\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\";\" data-imgfileid=\"100010546\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=715fe78d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F0m9F5vC1OGia42KIul6Uicy5FiaG8X1OwSS8rKdGacGlTzmQXkic9JQUpxHAfgF94ANyFx6KMxrxo7EvnWWZ1LN84xRgsmExYiartVg3floMRYqc%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n    <figcaption style=\"text-align: center;color: #888;font-size: 0.8em;\"></figcaption>\n   </figure>\n   <blockquote style=\"border-radius:6px;border-top:0.2px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);padding:1em 1em 1em 2em;border-right:0.2px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-left:4px solid #FA5151;font-style:italic;margin-bottom:1em;border-bottom:0.2px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);\">\n    <p style=\"margin:0;display:block;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:1em;\"><span leaf=\"\">完成以上步骤之后，记得在飞书开放平台配置好</span><code style=\"font-size: 90%;color: #d14;background: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);padding: 3px 5px;border-radius: 4px;\"><span leaf=\"\">长连接</span></code><span leaf=\"\">和&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font-size: 90%;color: #d14;background: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);padding: 3px 5px;border-radius: 4px;\"><span leaf=\"\">im.message.receive_v1</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;，并且再次发布Bot应用！！！</span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <h2 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"display: table;margin: 4em auto 2em;color: #fff;background: #FA5151;font-weight: bold;text-align: center;padding: 0.3em 1.2em;font-size: 19.5px;border-radius: 8px 24px 8px 24px;box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);\"><span leaf=\"\">三、在OpenClaw实体中添加Agent</span></h2>\n   <blockquote style=\"border-radius:6px;border-top:0.2px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);padding:1em 1em 1em 2em;border-right:0.2px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-left:4px solid #FA5151;font-style:italic;margin-bottom:1em;border-bottom:0.2px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);\">\n    <p style=\"margin:0;display:block;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:1em;\"><span leaf=\"\">假设你已经拥有了一个打通过飞书的OpenClaw实例</span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <span leaf=\"\">先输入&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font-size: 90%;color: #d14;background: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);padding: 3px 5px;border-radius: 4px;\"><span leaf=\"\">openclaw agents list</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;查看已经存在的OpenClaw Agent：</span>\n   <figure style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"Lzg4BM\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.28425925925925927\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\";\" data-imgfileid=\"100010555\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=be23a528&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F0m9F5vC1OGhuEe0cM13PXIyoiarkicbjupfaiaIPHqJOLteJib367KkwlQWDokUlqficicUZDn9raUicqndE1gasRSYy9rice7hu6a2Lxw43cOvI6icI%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n    <figcaption style=\"text-align: center;color: #888;font-size: 0.8em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\"> \n      <br> \n     </span>\n    </figcaption>\n   </figure>\n   <span leaf=\"\">然后输入&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font-size: 90%;color: #d14;background: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);padding: 3px 5px;border-radius: 4px;\"><span leaf=\"\">openclaw agents add &lt;id&gt;</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;来添加一个新的Agent （这里我填的‘id’是‘ops’）：</span>\n   <figure style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"fc2aoS\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.799074074074074\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\";\" data-imgfileid=\"100010549\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=eccf9188&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F0m9F5vC1OGjwSjl32gcDRsWgaBlXD6JH1pkZoewr7HYcV2t9onbxBYs7wzqPicSQulb5FzFKe3EZLWvmX4N83iaUwKNv0AacicAcsgmlBxibK9o%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n    <figcaption style=\"text-align: center;color: #888;font-size: 0.8em;\"></figcaption>\n   </figure>\n   <span leaf=\"\"> \n    <br> \n   </span><span leaf=\"\">中间有若干选项（我标记在截图中了）；然后需要给这个新添加的Agents选择大模型，以KIMI为例：</span>\n   <figure style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"Ogt63Q\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.9175925925925926\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\";\" data-imgfileid=\"100010554\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a04b9672&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F0m9F5vC1OGjY6ic6dnb4e1RguGMNu13cB92vzc9FiaboxNdXoeWXnpricKibE5IrcOqgkXWBUADRG49EI8GPDSsaHMw77Evk4059BtvHiaEvQptc%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n    <figcaption style=\"text-align: center;color: #888;font-size: 0.8em;\"></figcaption>\n   </figure>\n   <span leaf=\"\"> \n    <br> \n   </span><span leaf=\"\">在渠道选择这里选择“No”&nbsp;</span>\n   <figure style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"dNAwif\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2876712328767123\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"730\" style=\";\" data-imgfileid=\"100010552\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=414cf08b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F0m9F5vC1OGjqK1HgdFPQWCicU10pyMStlrD9TZr5qia0icuaGVBe73WoE6a34pQQQBibAa9GichjicBpgKbcBEW57zjmqEl0aCht5qqfbGWxDNvew%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n    <figcaption style=\"text-align: center;color: #888;font-size: 0.8em;\"></figcaption>\n   </figure>\n   <blockquote style=\"border-radius:6px;border-top:0.2px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);padding:1em 1em 1em 2em;border-right:0.2px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-left:4px solid #FA5151;font-style:italic;margin-bottom:1em;border-bottom:0.2px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);\">\n    <p style=\"margin:0;display:block;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:1em;\"><span leaf=\"\">当然，如果你足够熟练，以上步骤也可以直接在openclaw.json中修改（见\"list\"下添加的\"ops\"相关内容）：</span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <figure style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"bOmrgE\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.1157407407407407\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\";\" data-imgfileid=\"100010553\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=18706c90&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F0m9F5vC1OGg6jAOdx49joflia1ZnGTY3iaUibrbEQkaUrHRcia3SneT4BZSkJMvq1mzxmoYxjsrrGdDNDFoWRfviasnQLqPviczJ21SibbGUwvKYG8%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n    <figcaption style=\"text-align: center;color: #888;font-size: 0.8em;\"></figcaption>\n   </figure>\n   <h2 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"display: table;margin: 4em auto 2em;color: #fff;background: #FA5151;font-weight: bold;text-align: center;padding: 0.3em 1.2em;font-size: 19.5px;border-radius: 8px 24px 8px 24px;box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);\"><span leaf=\"\">四、打通（绑定） 新Agent 和 新飞书Bot【关键步骤】</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;\"><span leaf=\"\">在Terminal终端输入以下命令完成新添加的Agent和新添加的飞书channel的绑定（bind）：</span></p>\n   <pre style=\"border-radius:8px;border:1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);padding:0 !important;margin:10px 8px;font-size:90%;overflow-x:auto;line-height:1.5;\"><code data-language-pending=\"\" data-raw-code=\"openclaw agents bind --agent ops --bind feishu:ops\" data-show-line-number=\"false\" style=\"border-radius:4px;padding:0.5em 1em 1em;margin:0;text-indent:0;white-space:nowrap;display:-webkit-box;font-size:90%;overflow-x:auto;font-family:'Fira Code',\n    Menlo,\n    Operator Mono,\n    Consolas,\n    Monaco,\n    monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">openclaw agents bind --agent ops --bind feishu:ops</span></code></pre>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif;font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.75;text-align: left;\">\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;\" data-pm-slice=\"2 2 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif;font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.75;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span leaf=\"\">（我都起了相同的名字</span><code style=\"font-size: 90%;color: #d14;background: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);padding: 3px 5px;border-radius: 4px;\"><span leaf=\"\">ops</span></code><span leaf=\"\">，如果你起了其他名字</span><code style=\"font-size: 90%;color: #d14;background: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);padding: 3px 5px;border-radius: 4px;\"><span leaf=\"\">请替换为相应名称</span></code><span leaf=\"\">）</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif;font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.75;text-align: left;\">\n   <figure style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"MvQoCK\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3453703703703704\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\";\" data-imgfileid=\"100010559\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f75ad795&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F0m9F5vC1OGjxCYP84iaFqIQsPLDgKGrDKlXa3SoELTzdsaqfCFYB3P5JZsOR4aicN7biahDdibjuCz4icJqBcqm1fSRby42BC8ZUhB7FEtoG3PYU%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n    <figcaption style=\"text-align: center;color: #888;font-size: 0.8em;\"></figcaption>\n   </figure>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;\"><span leaf=\"\">然后，注意，需要重启gateway：</span></p>\n   <pre style=\"border-radius:8px;border:1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);padding:0 !important;margin:10px 8px;font-size:90%;overflow-x:auto;line-height:1.5;\"><code data-language-pending=\"\" data-raw-code=\"openclaw gateway restart\" data-show-line-number=\"false\" style=\"border-radius:4px;padding:0.5em 1em 1em;margin:0;text-indent:0;white-space:nowrap;display:-webkit-box;font-size:90%;overflow-x:auto;font-family:'Fira Code',\n    Menlo,\n    Operator Mono,\n    Consolas,\n    Monaco,\n    monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">openclaw gateway restart</span></code></pre>\n   <span leaf=\"\"> \n    <br> \n   </span><span leaf=\"\">第一轮对话会获得配对码，需要在命令行中运行&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font-size: 90%;color: #d14;background: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);padding: 3px 5px;border-radius: 4px;\"><span leaf=\"\">openclaw pairing approve feishu 配对码</span></code><span leaf=\"\">：</span>\n   <figure style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"o5Yht1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.30462962962962964\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-imgfileid=\"100010558\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ab2ac274&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F0m9F5vC1OGjmoIPCXOtsRoyrRSnQLiaOeWuCbRHunRVWTyN87ib1l9CWWYBfd04GXTuwnE3kRRYkUkUKCgGoibRCYh40J2MEe3MTV5hBicPRZDU%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n    <figcaption style=\"text-align: center;color: #888;font-size: 0.8em;\"></figcaption>\n   </figure>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif;font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.75;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\">再次提醒注意：如果没有重启Gateway，则会出现串台（见红框中内容，是旧的bot的回复）：</span>\n   <figure style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"X2NyKo\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.762962962962963\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\";\" data-imgfileid=\"100010561\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d13a8c05&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F0m9F5vC1OGhMtp3IBUrG0zsJnXPicUzduictWwspUod9oAw85yneiaYiaMWk2uVgjk2LQlIxc1zVEWjzAoVeroX6JicRkg9TdkSgibLcNXavWrLg0%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n    <figcaption style=\"text-align: center;color: #888;font-size: 0.8em;\"></figcaption>\n   </figure>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;\"><span leaf=\"\">重启Gateway后，就正常启动了第一轮对话的Bootstrap流程（给这个新的openclaw建人设，以及告知openclaw你自己的信息），见红框下方的对话。</span></p>\n   <hr style=\"border-style: solid;border-width: 2px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);height: 1px;border: none;margin: 2em 0;background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0));\">\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;\"><span leaf=\"\">此外，在openclaw.json中可以看到agents和workspace都存在两个就对了：</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"margin-left:0;padding-left:1.5em;list-style:none;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"margin:0.5em 8px;display:block;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">• agents有</span><code style=\"font-size: 90%;color: #d14;background: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);padding: 3px 5px;border-radius: 4px;\"><span leaf=\"\">main</span></code><span leaf=\"\">和</span><code style=\"font-size: 90%;color: #d14;background: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);padding: 3px 5px;border-radius: 4px;\"><span leaf=\"\">ops</span></code></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin:0.5em 8px;display:block;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">• workspace有不带后缀（就是</span><code style=\"font-size: 90%;color: #d14;background: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);padding: 3px 5px;border-radius: 4px;\"><span leaf=\"\">main</span></code><span leaf=\"\">)和带后缀的</span><code style=\"font-size: 90%;color: #d14;background: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);padding: 3px 5px;border-radius: 4px;\"><span leaf=\"\">-ops</span></code><span leaf=\"\"> \n       <br> \n      </span></p>\n     <figure style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"lY3G17\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.9081967213114754\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"610\" style=\"font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;background-color: transparent;width: 236px;height: 450px;\" data-imgfileid=\"100010556\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e0655f55&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F0m9F5vC1OGhaM2GhSh6ZXkMJ9TXbv9tUVAib8UU374ofyeCXSeJwr4MakWB9eHic1RCGMvNmxvYPE5MqGBjtponxxoV4lNuf3YYuPGj2Oma54%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n     </figure>\n     <p></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p></p>\n   <figure style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;\"></figure>\n   <p></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;\"><span leaf=\"\">OpenClaw提供了非常灵活的权限设置；比如，一个agent可以拥有全部权限，另一个agent却只能聊天，都可以直接在 openclaw.json中进行配置~</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;\"><span leaf=\"\">Anyway，我现在是过上“猫狗🦞双全”的好日子了~&nbsp;<img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"gGPHq5\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6138888888888889\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\";\" data-imgfileid=\"100010563\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=df1db222&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F0m9F5vC1OGjdkPllWmcoUYtJbH5Bm0YfB67psVMlejpiaNkA9cwxoWricKD5dhe3jJhcQl1zLbhMWXibKOBoeOcfLv1BduYibra7s2PGSxRXX0I%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n   <figcaption style=\"text-align: center;color: #888;font-size: 0.8em;\"></figcaption>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;\"><span leaf=\"\">祝大家和多个龙虾🦞玩耍愉快~</span></p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文详细介绍了如何在 OpenClaw 框架中通过配置 JSON 文件和 CLI 工具，实现单实例多 Agent 部署并绑定多个飞书 Bot 的实操流程。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文详细介绍了如何在 OpenClaw 框架中通过配置 JSON 文件和 CLI 工具，实现单实例多 Agent 部署并绑定多个飞书 Bot 的实操流程。",
  "summary": "文章主要讲解了 OpenClaw 框架的多 Agent 并行运行机制。作者通过四个核心步骤：在飞书开放平台创建应用、修改 `openclaw.json` 配置文件以支持多账号（accounts）结构、利用 CLI 命令添加新 Agent，以及执行关键的绑定（bind）操作，展示了如何在一个 OpenClaw 实例中管理多个具有独立人设、大模型配置和权限的机器人。文中特别强调了修改配置后的数据迁移、重启 Gateway 以及配对码验证等实操细节，旨在帮助用户在节省硬件资源的同时，实现多任务 AI 助手的并行运行。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "OpenClaw 框架原生支持多 Agent 并行运行机制。",
      "explanation": "允许在单一运行实例下挂载多个不同功能的 Agent，每个 Agent 可以独立对应不同的聊天软件渠道或账号，实现资源复用。"
    },
    {
      "point": "通过修改 openclaw.json 的 accounts 字段实现多渠道管理。",
      "explanation": "需要将原有的顶层凭证迁移至 accounts 列表下的特定标识符中，并注意删除原位置冗余字段以防配置冲突。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Agent 与 Channel 之间需要通过 bind 命令建立显式映射。",
      "explanation": "使用 `openclaw agents bind` 命令将特定的 Agent ID 与指定的飞书账号 ID 绑定，这是确保多机器人互不干扰的关键逻辑步骤。"
    },
    {
      "point": "配置变更后的 Gateway 重启是避免“串台”的必要操作。",
      "explanation": "若不重启网关服务，系统可能沿用旧的路由逻辑，导致新旧 Bot 消息处理混乱，重启后需重新完成配对码验证流程。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "OpenClaw 原生支持在一个实例下安装多个 Agent（并行多只🦞）。每个 Agent 可以对应不同聊天软件的渠道 channel。",
    "把你现在顶层的 appId / appSecret 挪进 accounts.default（挪进去之后删除原来位置的 appId 和 appSecret 否则会出问题）。",
    "注意，需要重启 gateway：openclaw gateway restart。如果没有重启 Gateway，则会出现串台。",
    "OpenClaw 提供了非常灵活的权限设置；比如，一个 agent 可以拥有全部权限，另一个 agent 却只能聊天。"
  ],
